# Copy to .env (gitignored) and fill in your PERSONAL TESTNET wallet:
#   PEGIN_MNEMONIC — BIP39 seed phrase (test wallet only, never real funds)
#   PEGIN_DID      — a DID that *this same wallet* created on testnet11
# Both must belong to the same wallet — lookup derives keys from the mnemonic and
# searches coinset for that wallet's on-chain DID.
# Used by demo-cli.mjs and the personal-wallet part of smoke-test.mjs.
# In CI, set both as pipeline secrets instead — env vars win over this file.
PEGIN_MNEMONIC="your twelve or twenty four word testnet seed phrase goes here ..."
PEGIN_DID="did:chia:1..."
